text: Evgeniya Ivanova (born 13 July 1991) is an Uzbekistani water polo player. She was a member of the Uzbekistan women's national water polo team. She played in the 2009 World Aquatics Championships, 2010 Asian Games, 2011 World Aquatics Championships, and 2013 World Aquatics Championships. == References == Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Uzbekistani water polo players
